snippet.title: De'Vine: Heavenly Acres Release Trailer!
snippet.description:
De'Vine: Heavenly Acres is releasing on Steam July 29th, 2022!
The original price point will be $15.00. Not sure if there will be a release sale.
Come check it out!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1516680/DeVine_Heavenly_Acres/
